{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":944969,"duration_api_ms":867372,"num_turns":116,"result":"Now let me produce the JSON response conforming to the `ExecutionPayload` schema:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"change_summary\": \"Hardened retry policy to prevent runs from exiting on transient backend failures. Increased retry limits (TransportFailure 3→5, SchemaValidationFailure 2→3, Timeout 2→3), added hard timeout enforcement on backend process invocations via tokio::time::timeout wrapping spawn_and_wait, introduced BinaryNotFound failure class for non-retryable exit code 127 and spawn NotFound errors, and added exponential backoff (5s base, 60s cap) between retry attempts with configurable policy support.\",\n  \"steps\": [\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Increased retry limits in retry_policy.rs: TransportFailure 3→5, SchemaValidationFailure 2→3, Timeout 2→3\",\n      \"order\": 1,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added hard timeout enforcement in process_backend.rs spawn_and_wait by wrapping I/O+wait in tokio::time::timeout using request.timeout, killing child on expiry via spawn_background_reap and returning FailureClass::Timeout\",\n      \"order\": 2,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added BinaryNotFound variant to FailureClass enum (domain.rs) with terminal retry rule, classified spawn ErrorKind::NotFound and exit code 127 as BinaryNotFound via new classify_exit_failure helper in process_backend.rs\",\n      \"order\": 3,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Added configurable exponential backoff to RetryPolicy (backoff_base=5s, backoff_cap=60s, with_no_backoff() for tests) and integrated into engine.rs retry loop via retry_policy.backoff_for_attempt()\",\n      \"order\": 4,\n      \"status\": \"completed\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"description\": \"Updated retry_policy_test.rs assertions for new limits and BinaryNotFound, 